			<attribute id="HowToTrigger" type="LSString" value="- Load up GustavDev/BGO_Main_A&#xD;&#xA;- Use &quot;oe SAM_Crypt&quot; and &quot;SetGlobalOsirisFlag WYR_SentientAmulet_Knows_ShirraIsInCrypt&quot;&#xD;&#xA;OR&#xD;&#xA;Use &quot;oe SAM_Start&quot;, talk to Sister Yannis in the Open Hand Temple after her discussion with Valeria, ask about Shirra Clarwen and then head down to the crypt.&#xD;&#xA;- Make sure you haven't read the plaque on Shirra's coffin or opened the tomb yet." />
			<attribute id="needLayout" type="bool" value="False" />
			<attribute id="nextNodeId" type="uint32" value="2" />
			<attribute id="synopsis" type="LSString" value="A companion reacts to entering the Open Hand Temple crypt after learning that Shirra Clarwen, granddaughter of the Mad Monk inside the Sentient Amulet, has passed away and is interred here." />
